title: My Way To Turn The Tide
alternative_titles: My Way To Turn The Tide
summary: Hou Xing, a poor young man, travels to another world by accident and possesses the body of a good-for-nothing. Someone is destroying his family the minute he comes to this world, and fortunately, he survives. However, he finds that his martial spirit on which he relies to fight is just a cute hamster. How will this miserable man start his way to reverse the situation?
